glio|language=Spanish|trans-title=On Self-Accusation, (or from the Italian, Humility: The Road towards God)}}\n* {{cite book|title=El verdadero poder es el servicio|year=2007|publisher=Editorial Claretiana|location=Buenos Aires|first=Jorge|last=Bergoglio|oclc=688511686|language=Spanish|trans-title=True Power Is Service}}\n* {{cite book|title=Seminario: las deudas sociales de nuestro tiempo: la deuda social seg\u00fan la doctrina de la iglesia|year=2009|publisher=EPOCA-USAL|location=Buenos Aires|isbn=9788493741235|first=Jorge|last=Bergoglio|language=Spanish|trans-title=Seminar: the Social Debts of Our Time: Social Debt According to Church Doctrine}}\n* {{cite book|title=Sobre el cielo y la tierra|year=2010|publisher=Editorial Sudamericana|location=Buenos Aires|isbn=9789500732932|first1=Jorge|last1=Bergoglio|first2=Abraham|last2=Skorka|authorlink2=Abraham Skorka|language=Spanish|trans-title=On Heaven and Earth|title-link=On Heaven and Earth}}; {{cite book|first1=Jorge|last1=Bergoglio|first2=Abraham|last2=Skorka|authorlink2=Abraham Skorka|title=On Heaven and Earth: Pope Francis on Faith, Family, and the Church in the Twenty-First Century|year=2013|publisher=Random House|location=New York|isbn=978-0770435066|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780770435066}}\n* {{cite book|title=Seminario Internacional: consenso para el desarrollo: reflexiones sobre solidaridad y desarrollo|year=2010|publisher=EPOCA|location=Buenos Aires|isbn=9789875073524|first=Jorge|last=Bergoglio|language=Spanish|trans-title=International seminar: Consensus about Development: Reflexions on Solidarity and development}}\n* {{cite book|title=Nosotros como ciudadanos, nosotros como pueblo: hacia un bicentenario en justicia y solidaridad|year=2011|publisher=Editorial Claretiana|location=Buenos Aires|isbn=9789505127443|first=Jorge|last=Bergoglio|language=Spanish|trans-title=Ourselves as Citizens, Ourselves as a People: towards a Bicentenary in Justice and Solidarity}}\n* {{cite bo