undo|year=1995|publisher=Argentina Catholic University: Faculty of Theology|first=Jorge|last=Bergoglio|language=Spanish|oclc=806712655|url=http://dialnet.unirioja.es/descarga/articulo/2489810.pdf}}\n* {{cite conference|title=Episcopus minister Evangelii Iesu Christi propter spem mundi: relatio post disceptationem|year=2001|publisher=E Civitate Vaticana|first1=Edward Michael|last=Egan|first2=Jorge|last2= Bergoglio|conference=The Catholic Church. The Synod of Bishops. Ordinary General Assembly|oclc=749998123}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Bergoglio|first1=Jorge|editor1-first=Elisa|editor1-last=Buzzi|title=A Generative Thought: An Introduction to the Works of Luigi Giussani|chapter-url=http://site.ebrary.com/id/10132858|year=2003|publisher=McGill-Queen's University Press |location=Montreal |isbn=978-0-7735-2612-9|pages=79\u201383|chapter=For Man}}\n* {{cite book|title=Di\u00e1logos entre Juan Pablo II y Fidel Castro|year=2004|publisher=Ciudad Argentina|location=Buenos Aires|isbn=9789875070745|editor-first=Jorge|editor-last=Bergoglio|first1=Pope|last1=John Paul|first2=Fidel|last2=Castro|language=Spanish|trans-title=Dialogues Between John Paul II and Fidel Castro}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Bergoglio|first=Jorge|year=2007|title=Buscar el camino hacia el futuro, llevando consigo la memoria de las ra\u00edces|journal=[[Humanitas (journal)|Humanitas]]|issue=47|pages=468\u2013483 |publisher=[[National Humanities Institute]]|language=Spanish|oclc=176911626}}\n* {{cite book|title=El santito Ceferino Namuncur\u00e1: relato en verso|year=2007|publisher=Lumen|location=Buenos Aires|first=Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda|last=Casti\u00f1eira de Dios|others=Foreword by Jorge Bergoglio|isbn=9789870007340|language=Spanish}}\n* {{cite book|last=Spadaro|first1=Antonio, SJ (interviewer)|title=A Big Heart Open to God: A Conversation with Pope Francis|year=2013|publisher=HarperOne|location=New York |isbn=978-0062333773}}\n* [https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/pont_committees/eucharist-congr/documents/rc_committ_